<h1 class="title">Teaching Committee</h1>

<div id="outline-container-org3a0ed39" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org3a0ed39"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> Synopsis</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
<p>
I serve as the undergraduate advisor and head of teaching committee for years 2&#x2013;4 (&#x202e;יועץ לתואר ראשון, ויו"ר ועדת הוראה לשנים ב–ד&#x202c;) at the <a href="//www.cs.bgu.ac.il/"><i>Department of Computer Science</i></a> at <a href="http://www.bgu.ac.il/"><i>Ben-Gurion University</i></a>. 
</p>
</div>
</div>

